                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>from her uncle <persName>Peixotto</persName> that <persName>Mr. Sarfaty</persName>\n                did not approve of my circular;<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr. S.</persName> by the way is a very intelligent man, but rather too\n                fond of setting<lb/> himself up as a literary judge and <sic>critick</sic>, and in\n                this way he has <sic>criticised</sic><lb/> some of my sermons which I allowed\n                    <persName>Simha</persName> to copy and send to him,<lb/> which however to me\n                appears rather ridiculous as his education<lb/> has been by no means one from which\n                a man could derive that<lb/> peculiar talent so requisite to form a correct judgment\n                of literary com-<lb/>positions, which is full as difficult as book-keeping or buying\n                &amp; selling<lb/> dry goods and groceries. Several people have spoken about sending\n                their<lb/> children but I know not whether they are coming or not. <persName>Miss\n                    Rebecca<lb/> Phillips</persName> desired me to convey to you her regrets at not\n                having seen you.<lb/> She sends her love, as do also many others.\n                    <persName>Theodore</persName> wrote to me and he<lb/> &amp;\n                    <persName>Myrtilla</persName> both desire their affectionate remembrance.\n                    <persName>Isaac Seixas</persName><lb/> inquires about you all in a letter I got\n                on <date>Monday</date>. <persName>Mr. Goldsmit</persName><lb/> &amp; <persName>Mr\n                    Hyneman</persName> were much gratified by your hospitality.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Give my love to aunt and all the rest. Not having any more time<lb/>\n                they must excuse me for being brief.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Your affectionate nephew</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\"><persName role=\"author\">Isaac Leeser</persName>.</p>"
                  },
